# Kubernetes Commands

Delete all resources

```
kubectl delete all --all
```

Check resources

```
kubectl get all
```

Deploy application

```
kubectl apply -f deployment.yml
```

Scale pods

```
kubectl scale deployment javawebdeploy --replicas=4
```

